       (9382, 2, 7206, 38, 'General', 'Email', 'BNP - Step 8:  Nomination', 'NTNP Nomination', 'noreply@gov.nt.ca', '',
        '',
        '<div>Hello&nbsp;&lt;%title%&gt; &lt;%last_name%&gt;,</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>I am very happy to advise that you have been officially approved for nomination under the Business Stream of the Northwest Territories Nominee Program (NTNP) &ndash; Congratulations!</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>Please find attached a confirmation letter regarding your nomination and your actual nomination certificate that must be submitted with your application for permanent residency. Please ensure that you apply for permanent residency by &lt;%nomination_certificate_expiry_date%&gt;&ndash; this is very important as the NTNP does not issue extensions for nomination certificates.</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>As well, please be advised that once you have submitted your application for permanent residency, you are able to apply for a bridging open work permit (if required).</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>In order to return your $75,000 Good Faith Deposit, you must be set up as a vendor to recieve direct deposit. Please fill out the the following two forms and return to NTNP staff.</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div><a class="yiv6631387874ydp81d61aa2yiv3615660690moz-txt-link-freetext" href="https://ntnp.immigratenwt.ca/Vendor%20Customer%20Setup%20Request%20Form.pdf" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(25, 106, 212); text-decoration: underline; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" target="_blank">https://ntnp.immigratenwt.ca/Vendor%20Customer%20Setup%20Request%20Form.pdf</a><br />\n<a class="yiv6631387874ydp81d61aa2yiv3615660690moz-txt-link-freetext" href="https://ntnp.immigratenwt.ca/Vendor%20Direct%20Deposit%20Authorization%20Form.pdf" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(25, 106, 212); text-decoration: underline; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" target="_blank">https://ntnp.immigratenwt.ca/Vendor%20Direct%20Deposit%20Authorization%20Form.pdf</a></div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>Such exciting news!&nbsp; Please contact NTNP staff directly if you have any questions.</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>Thank you,</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>NTNP Business Stream</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>',
