        '<div>Hello &lt;%title%&gt; &lt;%last_name%&gt;,&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>Please be advised that in advance of your Step 2: Further Investigations and Face-to-Face Interview scheduled on&nbsp;&lt;%interview_date%&gt;, you are required to submit a summary of your business concept to NTNP staff twenty-four (24) hours in advance of your interview.</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>Please note that the NTNP did not recieve&nbsp;a summary of your proposed business concept with your online BNP - Pre-Interview Submission. Please submit your business concept summary to NTNP Program Staff at the contact information below.&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>Thank you,</div>\n\n<div>&lt;%current_user_fName%&gt;&nbsp;&lt;%current_user_lName%&gt;&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>&lt;%current_user_email%&gt;</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>',
