        '<div>\n<div>Hello&nbsp;&lt;%title%&gt;&nbsp;&lt;%last_name%&gt;</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>Please be advised that the NTNP has still not recieved your online Step 3: Expression of Interest submission. As per the Business Stream Application Guidelines you are required to submit your Step 3: Expression of Interest information within sixty (60) days of being notified of a positive outcome for the Step 2: Face-to-Face interview.&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>Please note that you have&nbsp;<strong>one (1) week&nbsp;</strong>from today&#39;s date to compelete the &quot;BNP - Expression of Interst&quot; section of your online NTNP Application. If you do not submit the required information within the timeframe noted, your application will be closed.&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>If you are no longer interested in pursuing your application with the Business Stream of the NTNP, please advise program staff at the contact information below.</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>Thank you,</div>\n\n<div>&lt;%current_user_fName%&gt;&nbsp;&lt;%current_user_lName%&gt;</div>\n\n<div>&lt;%current_user_email%&gt;</div>\n</div>',
